#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/71/
msgid "海盗 - 手速倒转"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/71/
msgid "这个流派依赖于无限刷牌并找到某种方法将无限铸币转化为属性。 [[Fleet Admiral Tethys||101122]], [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] 和 [[Visionary Shipman||126810]] 的组合将为你产生无限铸币。购买每张会给你额外的铸币的卡，例如[[Sellemental||64038]]、[[Patient Scout||97604]]和[[Tad||87060]]来维持无限循环。最常见的是使用 [[Shore Marauder||127242]] 与其他海盗如[[Plankwalker||128086]] 的组合，在刷无限铸币的同时扩大你的棋盘属性。进阶技巧：在你的棋盘上保留一个[[Air Revenant||126173]]，当你看到[[Acid Rainfall||126171]] 时转酸雨流，成长速度会更快。或者你可以把海盗属性吃给[[Stuntdrake||127238]]，然后打出复仇随从。或者你可以用[[Forsaken Weaver||126733]]转攻击成长亡灵流。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/71/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + [[Fleet Admiral Tethys||101122]]/[[Visionary Shipman||126810]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/71/
msgid "[[Fleet Admiral Tethys||101122]]\n"
"[[Visionary Shipman||126810]]\n"
"[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/71/
msgid "Have infinite gold to scale"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/76/
msgid "野猪人 - 邪能手速"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/76/
msgid "要玩这个流派，你必须拥有极其庞大的经济。这通常通过第9回合就获得金色布莱恩·铜须，或早期铜须+远望船夫+舰队上将特塞斯来实现。当你经济过盛时，你可以在不缺铸币的情况下刷 [[Moon Bacon Jazzer||98930]], [[Fearless Foodie||113154]], 和 [[Briarback Drummer||126669]] 。这将使你的酒馆在整个游戏过程中不断成长。由于铜须和远望船夫的存在，你还会产生大量法术，让邪能野猪人能够反复吞食巨大的酒馆随从。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/76/
msgid "早期无限金币 + [[Paint Smudger||104768]]/[[Felboar||110664]] 来稳定战力，并最终找到邪能野猪人。"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/76/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]\n"
"[[Visionary Shipman||126810]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/76/
msgid "Cast spells to consume buffed shop."
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "亡灵 - 攻击提升"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "使用 [[Forsaken Weaver||126733]] 提升你的亡灵和召唤物的攻击力。最好的法术生成器是 [[Visionary Shipman||126810]]，也可以是其他形式的法术生成包括 [[Wintergrasp Ghoul||126955]]、[[Spirit Drake||128084]] 或 [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]。你的召唤物数量来自 [[Handless Forsaken||95265]] 和 [[Deathly Striker||115610]]。确保尽可能多地复生关键亡灵，从 [[Handless Forsaken||95265]] 开始复生。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "攻击提升 ([[Forsaken Weaver||126733]]) + 法术生成([[Visionary Shipman||126810]]/[[Spirit Drake||128084]]/[[Wintergrasp Ghoul||126955]])"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "[[Deathly Striker||115610]] \n"
"[[Spirit Drake||128084]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "Summon high attack Undeads"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/75/
msgid "元素 - 投球手"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/75/
msgid "这个策略涉及留在2级酒馆，购买你看到的每一个 [[Fire Baller||116736]] 和 [[Snow baller||117667]]。你还应该购买你看到的前5到8个钻探原油，以及每一个刷新法术。能带来经济收益的特定英雄在这个策略中远比普通英雄要强得多。克罗米可以购买所有 2 级法术，这会给你带来很多免费经济，努波顿每回合可以复制一个钻探原油，塞纳留斯每回合可以按英雄技能，库尔特鲁斯每回合可以得到一个免费投球手，而德纳修斯大帝可以得到时空干扰用这个策略是自动获胜。如果没有强大的英雄技能，你必须依赖一张好的时空扭曲卡，比如冰雪元素或弹跳鱼，否则就无法玩，而且你应该正常升级酒馆正常玩。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/75/
msgid "特定英雄或2级酒馆时空扭曲弹跳鱼/时空扭曲冰雪元素"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/75/
msgid "特定英雄"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/75/
msgid "Scale balls"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/44/
msgid "野兽 - 钻地虫"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/44/
msgid "必须很早就打出 [[Silithid Burrower||108547]] ，并有初始的复仇能力。用最初的2~3个回合把钻地虫养大，与此同时，逐步加入核心卡到阵容中。在你觉得合适时，去掉复仇组件而专注于触发 [[Silithid Burrower||108547]] 的亡语，例如 [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] 或 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]]。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/44/
msgid "很早就打出 [[Silithid Burrower||108547]] ，并有初始的复仇能力"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/44/
msgid "复仇能力 ([[Twilight Broodmother||127236]])"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/44/
msgid "Make huge beasts in combat"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/52/
msgid "亡灵 - 龟甲"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/52/
msgid "使用 [[Friendly Geist||120219]] 增强酒馆法术的攻击力，并通过 [[Carapace Raiser||122479]] 生成 [[Haunted Carapace||122489]] 法术。提图斯·瑞文戴尔至关重要，因为它能将这两种效果翻倍。这些法术既能强化你的棋盘，又能召唤大量攻击力，因此你需要让场上的其他随从成为召唤物生成者，例如[[Twilight Broodmother||127236]]。最后使用 [[Prosthetic Hand||112364]] 来复生你的核心亡灵随从。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/52/
msgid "[[Titus Rivendare||97408]]/[[Friendly Geist||120219]] + [[Carapace Raiser||122479]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/52/
msgid "[[Carapace Raiser||122479]]\n"
"[[Friendly Geist||120219]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/52/
msgid "Buff summons using spells."
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/17/
msgid "野猪人 - 战斗提升"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/17/
msgid "Scale up your gems in the midgame, usually using [[Sanguine Refiner||122566]] but [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Moon-Bacon Jazzer||98930]] works too. Then, pick up your core pieces for the Combat Scaling Quilboar board. [[Three lil' Quilboar||114486]] adds a ton of gems to your boars in combat, while [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] and [[Needling Crone||120035]] each are multipliers for this effect."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/17/
msgid "[[Three Lil' Quilboar||114486]] + 鲜血宝石属性成长([[Prickly Piper||98946]]/[[Sanguine Refiner||122566]])"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/17/
msgid "野猪中期过度([[Prickly Piper||98946]]/[[Bonker||70173]])"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/17/
msgid "Scale up blood gems, unleash them during combat"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "恶魔 - 伤害"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "[[Lord of the Ruins||122116]] buffs by having your demons deal damage to minions. The best way to do that is with [[Silent Enforcer||122605]] + [[Titus Rivendare||97408]], which damages all your opponent's minions at once. [[Devout Hellcaller||122586]] and [[Tarecgosa||72062]] are ways to get permanent scaling."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "[[Silent Enforcer||122605]] + 受伤回报 ([[Lord of the Ruins||122116]])"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "[[Lord of the Ruins||122116]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "Demons deal damage to buff board"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "机械 - 亡语"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "First, start generating volumizers using either [[Conveyor Construct||126816]] or Metal Dispenser. For these small volumizers, you should only sell them or triple them, no need to attach them. Then, with [[Apexis Guardian||126820]], put scaled volumizers on your mechs in combat. Reborning it double its power, and [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] and [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] further multiply the magnetic count. Every fight, your board will be better and better because each combat will scale volumizers for future combats. Rolling for board improvements is usually better than buying volumizers from shop."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "[[Conveyor Construct||126816]] + [[Apexis Guardian||126820]] + 瑞文/鹦鹉/复生"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "扩音机中期过度 ([[Conveyor Construct||126816]])"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "Magnetize huge magnetics in combat"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "纳迦 - 深沉蓝调"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "刷新酒馆只拿 [[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]], [[Zesty Shaker||99054]] 和 [[Flaming Enforcer||126924]]。将你的塑造法术施加在魔焰执行者上，以获得永久属性加成。 6级的 [[Bluesy Siren||127229]] 能进一步成长你的深沉蓝调并提供大量节奏。当你拥有所有金色版本后，用烈毒填充你棋盘的其余部分，例如  [[Leeroy the Reckless||90425]] 和 [[Daggerspine Thrasher||103714]]。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "早期获得 [[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]]/[[Bluesy Siren||127229]] + [[Zesty Shaker||99054]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "[[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]]\n"
"[[Zesty Shaker||99054]]\n"
"[[Bluesy Siren||127229]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "Scale Naga's spellcraft"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "机械 - 圣盾"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "Use [[Whirling Lass-o-Matic||110668]] primarily to generate spells. Then, use [[Charging Czarina||110321]] to convert these spells into attack buffs for your divine shields, such as [[Greasebot||72389]]."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "法术生成 ([[Whirling Lass-o-matic||110668]]) + [[Charging Czarina||110321]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "Divine Shields ([[Grease bot||72389]])"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "Play spells to buff Mechs"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/77/
msgid "野兽 - 邪能恐角龙"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/77/
msgid "Use [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Felhorn||129437]] to have your Felhorn deal damage to your minions multiple times. This will benefit your payoff cards such as [[Lord of the ruins||122116]], which buffs your whole board, or [[Silky Shimmermoth||121135]] which scales your beetles. [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]], reborn, [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]], [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] ALL provide multipliers for this effect, and stacking multipliers scales your board insanely fast. You usually use [[Refreshing Anomaly||64042]] instead of Felhorn at first to ramp up economy."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/77/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + 良好经济"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/77/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/77/
msgid "Deal damage to your own board to scale."
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/72/
msgid "野猪人 - 宝石弹幕"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/72/
msgid "First, scale your gems, typically through cycling [[Moon-bacon Jazzer||98930]] and [[Fearless Foodie||113154]] and keeping a [[Prickly Piper||98946]]. Then, scale shop using Gem Barrage. This is usually done with [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] + [[Razorfen Flapper||126667]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]], but could be done with [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Briarback Drummer||126669]] as well. Finally, the payoff for your buffed shops include [[Trench Fighter||126671]] so you can use your Gem Confiscation in shop to triple its stats, and [[Felboar||110664]] to eat buffed units in the shop."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/72/
msgid "宝石强化 ([[Prickly Piper||98946]]) + 剃刀沼泽舞扇者+ 属性转移 ([[Trench Fighter||126671]]/[[Felboar||110664]])"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/72/
msgid "宝石强化 ([[Prickly Piper||98946]]/[[Moon Bacon Jazzer||98930]])"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/72/
msgid "Make shop big with gems."
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/56/
msgid "鱼人 - 小学生"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/56/
msgid "这个流派依赖于教会魔鳍学徒一个强大的法术并不断触发它。[[Young Murk-eye||87084]] 是每回合触发这些法术的必备卡，其效果被 [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] 和 [[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]] 增强。教会学徒 [[Shiny ring||109230]]、[[Azerite Empowerment||109232]] 或 [[Time management||117573]]，并搭配一些法强，这些法强来自 [[Felfire Conjurer||120299]]。在早期，教它一些经济法术也不错，特别是[[Strike Oil||104029]]。这个流派中不要三连小瞎眼！这不会增加你的身材。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/56/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + [[Magicfin Mycologist||122277]] + [[Young Murk-eye||87084]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/56/
msgid "[[Magicfin Mycologist||122277]]\n"
"[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/56/
msgid "Teach Murlocs spells and proc them"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/36/
msgid "Nalaa"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/36/
msgid "Buy every single spell that effectively costs 1 (Fleeting Vigor, Enchanted Lasso), to scale your good menagerie units. [[Stuntdrake||127238]] and [[Niuzao||103591]] are the most important cards to scale. Eventually, you can replace your worst units with summons such as [[Twilight Broodmother||127236]] to help support the [[Stuntdrake||127238]]."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/36/
msgid "[[Nalaa the Redeemer||104468]] + 酒馆法术生成 ([[Visionary Shipman||126810]])/优秀种族 ([[Whirling Lass-o-matic||110668]])"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/36/
msgid "[[Nalaa the Redeemer||104468]]\n"
"酒馆法术生成"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/36/
msgid "Buy spells to scale Menagerie units."
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "亡灵 - 挤爆"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "When the [[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]] deathrattle gets triggered, it'll buff your whole board via the [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] + [[Catacomb Crasher||114379]] combo. Use [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] to further proc Cadaver's deathrattle. Instead of [[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]], you may also use [[Lava Lurker||80747]] if you've stacked it with a lot of [[Surf n' Surf||103674]] deathrattles early."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "挤爆随从 ([[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]]) + [[Catacomb Crasher||114379]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "[[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]]\n"
"[[Lava Lurker||80747]] + [[Surf n' Surf||103674]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "Overflow your board to scale"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/79/
msgid "机械 - 摄影炸弹"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/79/
msgid "首先，你需要一个法术生成器。通常情况下，它是通过 [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + [[Visionary Shipman||126810]] + 另一张经济卡，例如 [[Fleet Admiral Tethys||101122]] 来实现的。这既能为你提供经济能力，让你找到你的摄影炸弹组合，又能同时强化它。[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Shell Collector||80740]] 或者 [[Rodeo Performer||104466]] 也可以用于法术生成。在中期，你可以使用 [[Nalaa the Redeemer||104468]] 或 [[Plankwalker||128086]] 来稳定局势。记得要复生嘲讽你的 [[Photobomber||113940]]。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/79/
msgid "酒馆法术生成 ([[Visionary Shipman||126810]]) + [[Photobomber||113940]])"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/79/
msgid "酒馆法术生成"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/79/
msgid "Scale your bombs and unleash them."
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "野兽 - 自伤"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "使用 [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]] 的组合每回合生成大量野兽。[[Monstrous Macaw||62230]], [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]], 复生和 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] 都能增强此效果。当你用 [[Rabid Panther||127111]] + [[Iridescent Skyblazer||107937]] 或双狂乱的猎豹建立起成长体系时，开始购买所有野兽来扩大你的棋盘。"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]] + [[Rabid Panther||127111]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]]\n"
"[[Rabid Panther||127111]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "Cycle beasts to damage themselves and scale"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/69/
msgid "元素 - 最右强化"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/69/
msgid "首先使用 [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Refreshing Anomaly||64042]] + [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] 进行无限刷新。再加入 [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] 和 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] 等放大器。有了这么多经济优势，开始循环并触发 [[En-Djinn Blazer||126175]] 来大幅强化最右边的随从。[[Acid Rainfall||126171]] 是你的强化最右边随从后的主要收益。如果你不选择双头飞龙，可以选择用 [[Fleet Admiral Tethys||101122]] 和 [[Visionary Shipman||126810]] 来花费铸币，然后用 [[Acid Rainfall||126171]] 强化右边的随从。"
